text: Bruno Trojani (29 August 1907 - 14 January 1966) was a Swiss ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1928 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1907 births Category:1966 deaths Category:Swiss male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Switzerland Category:Ski jumpers at the 1928 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
